    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have to see this absolute beauty! I've taken such good care of this car, it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's been totally babied\u2014garage-kept, smoke-free, and meticulously maintained. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! It's such a smooth ride and everything is in pristine shape. Come take it for a spin and fall in love! \u2728",
