    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving the depth and luster of its original factory paint, which remains free of swirls, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather seats show zero signs of wear, the bolsters are firm, and the interior still carries that new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by factory-trained technicians using only OEM parts. It has never seen rain, let alone snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example of automotive excellence that satisfies even the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
