      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83d\udc4b Honestly, it\u2019s tough to let this one go! This beauty is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, always kept in the garage and pampered. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
