      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 masterpiece. It features the factory-original Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a 3.64 ratio limited-slip differential. The 3.2L inline-six remains in peak operating condition, with the double-VANOS system recently overhauled and the rod bearing service completed as preventative maintenance. The chassis is impeccably preserved; the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral G-loads. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior retains its factory matte finish. This is a turn-key collector piece with the linear power delivery and razor-sharp throttle response that defines the golden era of M-division engineering.",
